      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Feeling unwell despite having asthma is worth addressing. As you age, lung function naturally declines, making it more challenging to breathe. Although it's possible that your age could be contributing, it's essential to review your inhaler usage and adjust as needed. Consult with your doctor to assess your asthma management and potentially reassess your inhaler. They can help determine if your symptoms are related to any medication issues.",
